data.description: Great opportuniity to own a 2 family in Southington! Welcome to 50-52 Prospect St, a residence that seamlessly blends smart living with an ingenious investment opportunity. This property not only provides a home but opens the door to living practically for free. Imagine purchasing furniture and transforming one floor into a short or medium-term rental, creating a harmonious mix of lifestyle and income.This home boasts features like city sewer and city water, two Navien Propane Super High Efficiency Combination Propane Boilers (installed in 2018, a modern paint job above the red brick exterior, and steel beam construction. The walk-up, insulated attic, two driveways accommodating up to 8 cars, and interior stairway access between apartments enhance both accessibility and comfort. Recently insulated between floors, the property showcases updated bathrooms with an industrial modern look.Situated within a few hundred feet of the Rails to Trails walking path and just a short distance to downtown Plantsville and downtown Southington, this residence offers so much. Enjoy the added benefit of two large 1320 sq ft 3-bedroom apartments. The strategic location, just 2 minutes from I-84 and 4 minutes from I-691, ensures optimal connectivity. Live smart, invest wisely – 50-52 Prospect St invites you to experience a lifestyle where modernity meets financial savvy. This gem is your ticket to a home that not only meets your needs but also pays you back.H & B by 1/30/24 @12 noon.
